c chó ăn có ngon không em?\"<span class=\"_5mfr _47e3\"><img class=\"img\" src=\"https://www.facebook.com/images/emoji.php/v8/fec/1/16/1f334.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" /><span class=\"_7oe\">????</span></span>\r\n<span class=\"_5mfr _47e3\"><img class=\"img\" src=\"https://www.facebook.com/images/emoji.php/v8/fec/1/16/1f334.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" /><span class=\"_7oe\">????</span></span>\"Hạt mắc ca với óc chó cái nào ngon hơn em?\"<span class=\"_5mfr _47e3\"><img class=\"img\" src=\"https://www.facebook.com/images/emoji.php/v8/fec/1/16/1f334.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" /><span class=\"_7oe\">????</span></span>\r\n<span class=\"_5mfr _47e3\"><img class=\"img\" src=\"https://www.facebook.com/images/emoji.php/v8/fec/1/16/1f334.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" /><span class=\"_7oe\">????</span></span>\"Hạt chia ăn có mùi vị gì không vậy em ?\"<span class=\"_5mfr _47e3\"><img class=\"img\" src=\"https://www.facebook.com/images/emoji.php/v8/fec/1/16/1f334.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" /><span class=\"_7oe\">????</span></span>\r\n<span class=\"_5mfr _47e3\"><img class=\"img\" src=\"https://www.facebook.com/images/emoji.php/v8/fec/1/16/1f334.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" /><span class=\"_7oe\">????</span></span>\"Hạt hạnh nhân ăn có béo lắm không em?\"<span class=\"_5mfr _47e3\"><img class=\"img\" src=\"https://www.facebook.com/images/emoji.php/v8/fec/1/16/1f334.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" /><span class=\"_7oe\">????</span></span>\r\n<span class=\"_5mfr _47e3\"><img class=\"img\" src=\"https://www.facebook.com/images/emoji.php/v8/fec/1/16/1f334.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" /><span class=\"_7oe\">????</span></span>\"Hạt chia uống nhiều có tốt không em?\"<span class=\"_5mfr _47e3\"><img class=\"img\" src=\"https://www.facebook.com/images/emoji.php/v8/fec/1/16/1f334.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" /><span class=\"_7oe\">????</span></span>\r\n<div class=\"text_